beer.beer_description: The Wayward Son Lupulin IPA was brewed specially for our head brewer's baby boy, Austin. This Hazy IPA was made using a new hop powder, called LupuLN2, which is the concentrated lupulin of whole-leaf hops containing resins and aromatic oils. It is designed to provide intense hop flavor and aroma, enabling brewers to dose large quantities of hops without introducing astringent flavors. The result is a fruit forward IPA with notes of apricot, pine, passion fruit and mango.
